OL,5, Whoopi Goldberg is facing a backlash   
OL,6, after she said on a US talk show that  
OL,7, the Holocaust "was not about race".    
OL,9,FThe actress and television personality 
OL,10,Fsaid on ABC's The View that the Nazi   
OL,11,Fgenocide of the Jews involved "two     
OL,12,Fgroups of white people".               
OL,14,FCritics pointed out that Hitler himself
OL,15,Fhad vented his hatred of the Jews in   
OL,16,Fracial terms. She later apologised.    
OL,18,FThe Nazis, who believed themselves an  
OL,19,FAryan "master race", murdered six      
OL,20,Fmillion Jews in the Holocaust.         
